f large $L^2$ norm. The analytical results are\nconfirmed by numerical approximations of the ground state on the dumbbell\ngraph.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Sep 2015 20:08:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Dec 2015 18:50:42 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 13 Oct 2017 14:50:39 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 24 Oct 2017 16:54:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-25"}
