ormation. DRX grains\nare revealed to form at both grain boundaries and junctions (e.g., quadruple\njunctions) and tend to maintain a triple line with old grains during the\ngrowth. The resulted stress redistribution is found to have a profound\ninfluence on the subsequent dislocation evolution and the softening.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Sep 2015 15:45:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Dec 2015 16:03:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-04"}
